# AHU lib modules

- **`ahu-recalc-params.ts`**: Shape of `ahuRecalcParams` JSON; keep in sync with UI and recalculate API body.
- **`ahu-recalc-validation.ts`**: Scope and dimension rules — changing validation requires coordinated UI copy.
- **`ahu-segment-costing.ts`**: Orchestrates blocks; calls `lib/calculations/*`.
- **`project-rollup.ts` / `cost-summary.ts`**: Project-level HPP and selling — do not double-apply margin.

See also **`costing-calculations.mdc`** for pure calculation files under `lib/calculations/`.
